Experimental stuff inspired by games like Stacklands. My dumbed down take on that concept.

Loading may take a while because the script is grabbing images from pollinations.ai. Sometimes pollinations gets overloaded/goes down, which results in the images not being visible.

Combining makes the AI aware of the cards' name and allows them to remove that card or add a new one. Once you're done combining, just send your message.
}}

{{char}} simulates the reactions of each combination of entities and uses them to create interesting stories.

